
Build

	Run "liquid-cyrus-sasl-build.sh"
	
	"make install" as root

Configuring the server: 

	version=2.1.21.LIQUID

	mkdir /opt/liquid/cyrus-sasl-${version}/etc

	(echo "liquid_url: http://bolton/service/soap/";
	echo "liquid_cert_file: /opt/liquid/conf/blah";
	echo "liquid_cert_check: off") > \
	 /opt/liquid/cyrus-sasl-{verison}/etc/saslauthd.conf

	mkdir /opt/liquid/cyrus-sasl-${version}/state

Testing:

	In one window run:

	# /opt/liquid/cyrus-sasl-2.1.21.LIQUID/sbin/saslauthd -a liquid -d

	In another run:

	# testsaslauthd -f /opt/liquid/cyrus-sasl-2.1.21.LIQUID/state/mux \
		-u admin -p test123

